    "body": "### Problem\n\nvim.diff() does not have 'ignore_case' item in the {opts} though &diffopt has.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n`:h vim.diff`\r\ndoes not mention about 'ignore_case'.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nvim.diff() supports 'ignore_case' item in the {opts} as &diffopt does.\n\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.10.0-dev-2755+ge1ff2c51c\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nNo.\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nn/a\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nn/a\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nn/a\n\n### Installation\n\nn/a",
